00:19:47.320 --> 00:19:49.640
'Lakshmi, apa yang kamu
lakukan begitu lama?'

00:19:51.080 --> 00:19:52.400
Siapa disana?

00:19:56.600 --> 00:19:57.560
Jika kamu...

